text: Yshmael Sali is a Filipino politician from the province of Tawi-Tawi, Philippines. He currently serves as Governor of the province. He was first elected as Governor in 2019. ==References== ==External links== *Province of Tawi-Tawi Category:Living people Category:National Unity Party (Philippines) politicians Category:People from Tawi-Tawi Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Filipino Muslims
